OL,5,G1600 The Motorway
OL,6,     FMotorway patrollers race to a car
OL,7,     Ffire on the M60, fearing that
OL,8,     Fsomeone may be trapped inside, and
OL,9,     Fan HGV runs over a rogue
OL,10,     Fwheelbarrow.
OL,11,G1700 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,12,G     Speeders
OL,13,     FAt Grimsby docks, Sergeant Tom
OL,14,     FElvidge pursues teenagers
OL,15,     Fsuspected of trying to steal a
OL,16,     Fmoped. With no time to wait for
OL,17,     Fbackup, a solo Tom chases after
OL,18,     Fthem.
