OL,5,G2000 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,6,G     Speeders
OL,7,     FAfter reports come in of two men
OL,8,     Farmed with sledgehammers trying to
OL,9,     Fbreak into a supermarket, police
OL,10,     Frace to the scene to intercept
OL,11,     Fthem, along with the dog unit.
OL,12,G2100 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FThis episode hits the ground
OL,14,     Frunning as the interceptors pull
OL,15,     Fover a driver, who casually steps
OL,16,     Fout of the car, before taking off
OL,17,     Flike a shot.
